---
title: Vanilla Poached Pears & Nutty Crumble with Yoghurt & Berry Compote | Serves 2
description: For a light brunch bite that everyone will love, look no further. We've combined tender vanilla poached pears, creamy yoghurt
and berry compote and topped them with a crunchy nutty crumble. Mornings never tasted so good!
